        <h1>Better PDF</h1><br/>
        Allows to place a link in a dashboard that generates the data as .pdf file and provides a variety of formating settings like a company logo and can include a chartsheet of your data according to your wishes.<br/>
        See a few examples below to ilustrate what can be achieved with relatively little effort. In adition to the global formating options set under "Formating settings" you can add options in the download link including charting and table formating options. Please see a few easy examples below.
        <p/><br/>
        <table>
